WEBVTT

00:03:28.508 --> 00:03:30.958
Tu so možgani ne-odlašalca.

00:03:30.958 --> 00:03:32.115
[Racionalni odločevalec]

00:03:32.115 --> 00:03:34.109
(Smeh)

00:03:34.133 --> 00:03:35.284
Tu pa...

00:03:36.325 --> 00:03:37.535
tu so moji možgani.

00:03:37.535 --> 00:03:39.445
[Opica instantne zadovoljitve]

00:03:39.445 --> 00:03:41.006
(Smeh)

00:03:43.713 --> 00:03:45.277
Razlika je.

00:03:45.904 --> 00:03:48.292
Oba imata v sebi Racionalnega odločevalca,

00:03:48.316 --> 00:03:49.968
a v možganih odlašalca

00:03:49.992 --> 00:03:52.978
je tudi Opica instantne zadovoljitve.

00:03:53.002 --> 00:03:55.304
Kaj to pomeni za odlašalca?

00:03:55.328 --> 00:03:57.769
Vse je v redu, dokler se ne zgodi tole.

00:03:57.793 --> 00:04:00.415
[Zdaj je odličen čas, da opraviva
nekaj dela.] [Ne!]